<h1>PII - Personal Identifiable Information<h1/>

Topics:
Ticket
PDF Key Value Document, other documents
Email

<h2>Access</h2>
<p>Grant operations groups permission <b>user.action.pii</b> to allow them to generate a PIIReportTicket for a user.</p>
<p>Grant end user groups permissoin <b>menu.read.pii-report</b> to access to the <b>Settings</b> menu <b>PII Report</b> which allows the user to generate and email themselves their PII Report</p>
